00:13:26,800 --> 00:13:27,800
Sorry, buddy,

295
00:13:27,800 --> 00:13:29,600
I left that life behind long ago.

296
00:13:30,520 --> 00:13:31,600
I never said

297
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:33,460
I wanted you to use shady tactics.

298
00:13:36,040 --> 00:13:36,760
Do I look like

299
00:13:36,760 --> 00:13:38,560
someone who knows any other way?

300
00:13:38,680 --> 00:13:40,280
I'm just brainstorming with you.

301
00:13:40,280 --> 00:13:41,160
Please don't bother me.

302
00:13:41,160 --> 00:13:42,890
I'm swamped. Look at this line.

303
00:13:46,800 --> 00:13:47,640
Want green onions?

304
00:13:47,640 --> 00:13:48,120
Yes.

305
00:13:49,160 --> 00:13:50,280
This morning, all the suppliers

306
00:13:50,280 --> 00:13:51,040
called me.

307
00:13:51,040 --> 00:13:52,080
They said they're going to sue us.

308
00:13:52,080 --> 00:13:53,760
Sue us!

309
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:55,760
And you're still smiling.

310
00:13:55,760 --> 00:13:56,600
You're grinning like an idiot.

311
00:13:56,600 --> 00:13:58,260
That stupid grin on your face.

312
00:13:59,000 --> 00:13:59,760
Liu.

313
00:14:00,200 --> 00:14:01,040
Tell me,

314
00:14:01,160 --> 00:14:02,680
what major company

315
00:14:02,760 --> 00:14:04,090
doesn't have lawsuits?

316
00:14:04,400 --> 00:14:06,160
They are major companies.

317
00:14:06,520 --> 00:14:07,920
You're just a big fraud.

318
00:14:08,480 --> 00:14:09,740
Your phone is ringing.

319
00:14:15,160 --> 00:14:15,720
Liu,

320
00:14:16,560 --> 00:14:18,420
please step outside for a moment.

321
00:14:22,960 --> 00:14:23,720
Hello.

322
00:14:23,800 --> 00:14:24,860
What are you doing?

323
00:14:24,920 --> 00:14:26,560
Why did it take you so long to answer?

324
00:14:26,560 --> 00:14:28,480
I was in a board meeting.

325
00:14:29,040 --> 00:14:31,000
Board meeting my ass!

326
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:32,730
When are you paying me back?

327
00:14:34,040 --> 00:14:35,280
I need to

328
00:14:35,280 --> 00:14:37,240
consult with the board to make decisions.

329
00:14:37,240 --> 00:14:37,800
This isn't something

330
00:14:37,800 --> 00:14:39,280
I can decide on my own.

331
00:14:40,360 --> 00:14:42,040
Look,

332
00:14:42,040 --> 00:14:42,560
could you please

333
00:14:42,560 --> 00:14:44,000
be more polite when talking to me?

334
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:46,000
I've been plenty polite with you.

335
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:47,920
You've been promising to pay for a month now.

336
00:14:47,920 --> 00:14:49,560
I haven't seen a penny yet.

337
00:14:49,560 --> 00:14:50,560
Who do you think you're talking to?

338
00:14:50,560 --> 00:14:52,360
Damn it!

339
00:14:52,360 --> 00:14:53,280
Don't talk to me like that.

340
00:14:53,280 --> 00:14:53,920
It's irritating.

341
00:14:53,920 --> 00:14:55,120
Who do you think you are?

342
00:14:55,120 --> 00:14:58,240
Have I disrespected you?

343
00:14:58,920 --> 00:15:00,520
Talk to me properly, you hear me?

344
00:15:00,520 --> 00:15:02,080
You little punk, where are you?

345
00:15:02,080 --> 00:15:03,120
I'm coming to find you right now.

346
00:15:03,120 --> 00:15:04,000
I'm at the company.

347
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:04,920
Come on over. I'll be waiting.

348
00:15:04,920 --> 00:15:05,880
Fine. Wait for me.

349
00:15:05,880 --> 00:15:06,640
Don't you dare run away.

350
00:15:06,640 --> 00:15:07,300
I won't run.

351
00:15:07,840 --> 00:15:09,900
If you don't show up, you're a coward.

352
00:15:20,080 --> 00:15:21,720
Why do you keep calling?

353
00:15:21,920 --> 00:15:23,040
Someone might come

354
00:15:23,040 --> 00:15:24,360
to collect debt by force.

355
00:15:24,360 --> 00:15:25,490
How did this happen?

356
00:15:25,680 --> 00:15:27,040
Can you find some guys

357
00:15:27,040 --> 00:15:28,280
to help me deal with this?

358
00:15:28,280 --> 00:15:29,080
Where are you?

359
00:15:29,640 --> 00:15:30,640
I'm at the office.

360
00:15:31,240 --> 00:15:32,320
Okay, got it.

361
00:15:38,120 --> 00:15:39,400
He's a man

362
00:15:39,840 --> 00:15:40,640
and he's blind.

363
00:15:40,640 --> 00:15:41,800
What are you going to do?

364
00:15:41,800 --> 00:15:44,080
This guy looks so familiar.

365
00:15:44,080 --> 00:15:45,680
Where have I seen him before?

366
00:15:45,760 --> 00:15:47,220
You were in jail together.

367
00:15:49,800 --> 00:15:50,520
Come with me. I need your help.

368
00:15:50,520 --> 00:15:51,320
What for?

369
00:15:51,320 --> 00:15:52,760
To solve some debt issues.

370
00:15:52,760 --> 00:15:54,490
You've already taken this job?

371
00:16:08,400 --> 00:16:09,920
Let's go.

372
00:16:18,160 --> 00:16:19,040
Why are they leaving?

373
00:16:19,040 --> 00:16:20,760
Abandoning the stall?

374
00:16:23,760 --> 00:16:25,090
What about my pancakes?

375
00:16:28,520 --> 00:16:30,050
Everyone should leave now.

376
00:16:31,800 --> 00:16:33,600
How can you just leave like that?

377
00:16:35,200 --> 00:16:37,330
You still owe me three months' salary.

378
00:16:38,600 --> 00:16:40,660
I'll definitely pay you your salary.

379
00:16:41,640 --> 00:16:42,680
Let's wrap this up.

380
00:16:42,680 --> 00:16:43,800
If I don't get my salary back,

381
00:16:43,800 --> 00:16:45,460
my wife and kids will leave me.

382
00:16:45,920 --> 00:16:47,240
Brother Liu, you don't need to be so upset.

383
00:16:47,240 --> 00:16:48,200
Boss, if you don't pay up,

384
00:16:48,200 --> 00:16:49,280
I'll deal with you too.

385
00:16:49,280 --> 00:16:50,560
Do you actually want to work for him?

386
00:16:50,560 --> 00:16:51,880
I'll do whatever I want.

387
00:16:51,880 --> 00:16:52,960
Alright, everyone calm down.

388
00:16:52,960 --> 00:16:54,440
I understand how you feel.

389
00:16:54,960 --> 00:16:55,840
But,

390
00:16:55,840 --> 00:16:57,840
some debt collectors are coming soon

391
00:16:57,840 --> 00:16:59,400
threatening to wreck our company.

392
00:16:59,400 --> 00:17:01,460
I don't want to drag you all into this.

393
00:17:03,600 --> 00:17:04,960
As for me...

394
00:17:06,160 --> 00:17:08,160
No, Brother Liu, what are you doing?

395
00:17:09,079 --> 00:17:10,240
I'll keep this for now.

396
00:17:10,240 --> 00:17:11,560
Take it home and have a look.

397
00:17:11,560 --> 00:17:13,220
Can you even carry that thing?

398
00:17:14,040 --> 00:17:15,170
Where's the remote?

399
00:17:16,960 --> 00:17:19,690
I'll bring it back when you're on your feet again.

400
00:17:20,880 --> 00:17:22,410
What kind of person is this?

401
00:17:23,480 --> 00:17:25,839
Boss, I believe you'll bounce back.

402
00:17:26,280 --> 00:17:27,010
Stay strong!

403
00:17:27,520 --> 00:17:28,160
Thanks.

404
00:17:37,360 --> 00:17:38,120
Uncle.

405
00:17:38,720 --> 00:17:40,040
Uncle, where are you?

406
00:17:40,040 --> 00:17:41,100
Coming right away.

407
00:17:41,120 --> 00:17:42,720
Your uncle says he's coming.

408
00:17:44,640 --> 00:17:45,440
What's up?

409
00:17:47,720 --> 00:17:48,880
Hey, you know,

410
00:17:49,680 --> 00:17:50,720
don't you have some buddies in the streets?

411
00:17:50,720 --> 00:17:52,280
Get a few of them over here.

412
00:17:52,360 --> 00:17:53,120
Who?

413
00:17:54,200 --> 00:17:54,880
Dapeng.

414
00:17:54,880 --> 00:17:55,880
Dapeng?

415
00:17:56,160 --> 00:17:57,220
Dapeng won't work.

416
00:17:57,720 --> 00:17:58,720
I heard that Dapeng

417
00:17:58,720 --> 00:18:00,760
got into some trouble a few years back,

418
00:18:00,760 --> 00:18:01,560
got caught,

419
00:18:01,560 --> 00:18:02,400
and they broke his leg.

420
00:18:02,400 --> 00:18:03,320
Broke his leg?

421
00:18:05,040 --> 00:18:05,760
What about Xiaofei?

422
00:18:05,760 --> 00:18:06,840
Xiaofei?

423
00:18:06,840 --> 00:18:08,880
He became a thief years ago.

424
00:18:08,880 --> 00:18:10,340
Got locked up a while back.

425
00:18:10,360 --> 00:18:12,400
Zhuzi's got a big crew.

426
00:18:12,400 --> 00:18:13,280
Zhuzi won't work either.

427
00:18:13,280 --> 00:18:14,240
I think Zhuzi

428
00:18:14,240 --> 00:18:16,120
works at some farm now,

429
00:18:16,120 --> 00:18:17,160
as a feeder

430
00:18:17,400 --> 00:18:18,730
out in the countryside.

431
00:18:18,760 --> 00:18:19,920
How did they all end up like this?

432
00:18:19,920 --> 00:18:20,380
Come on!

433
00:18:20,640 --> 00:18:21,960
What are you talking about?

434
00:18:21,960 --> 00:18:22,680
'End up like this'?

435
00:18:22,680 --> 00:18:23,920
Let me tell you, among all the guys,

436
00:18:23,920 --> 00:18:25,200
I'm doing the best now.

437
00:18:25,200 --> 00:18:25,920
I earn my living through honest work.

438
00:18:25,920 --> 00:18:26,680
But I'm just

439
00:18:26,680 --> 00:18:28,160
a pancake vendor, right?

440
00:18:28,240 --> 00:18:29,040
Isn't that?

441
00:18:29,520 --> 00:18:31,040
No, why are you asking me all this?

442
00:18:31,040 --> 00:18:31,920
Where are we going?

443
00:18:31,920 --> 00:18:32,520
You've got me confused.

444
00:18:32,520 --> 00:18:33,080
You just said 'let's go'

445
00:18:33,080 --> 00:18:33,920
so I came right away.

446
00:18:33,920 --> 00:18:34,680
It's just a small matter.

447
00:18:34,680 --> 00:18:36,040
Take off your apron first.

448
00:18:36,040 --> 00:18:36,560
When we get there,

449
00:18:36,560 --> 00:18:37,400
act like those tough guys

450
00:18:37,400 --> 00:18:38,480
from the 90s.

451
00:18:38,480 --> 00:18:39,760
Hey, who are you

452
00:18:39,760 --> 00:18:40,760
calling a thug?

453
00:18:40,880 --> 00:18:41,240
No, no.

454
00:18:41,240 --> 00:18:41,760
Who's a thug?

455
00:18:41,760 --> 00:18:42,620
I mean show some

456
00:18:42,760 --> 00:18:44,290
heroic spirit, that's all.

457
00:18:44,320 --> 00:18:46,040
That's more like it.

458
00:18:50,240 --> 00:18:51,280
After being inside

459
00:18:51,280 --> 00:18:52,120
for so long,

460
00:18:52,120 --> 00:18:54,240
do you know anyone tough

461
00:18:54,240 --> 00:18:55,770
who can intimidate people?

462
00:18:57,480 --> 00:18:58,960
How about Scarface Ming?

463
00:18:59,240 --> 00:19:00,320
I've heard of him.

464
00:19:00,640 --> 00:19:01,520
He scares everyone.

465
00:19:01,520 --> 00:19:02,520
He'll do.

466
00:19:02,520 --> 00:19:03,160
He's perfect.

467
00:19:03,160 --> 00:19:03,680
Get him.

468
00:19:03,680 --> 00:19:04,400
He's serving life.

469
00:19:04,400 --> 00:19:05,520
At least 20 more years.

470
00:19:05,520 --> 00:19:06,200
If you need him urgently,

471
00:19:06,200 --> 00:19:08,000
you two can help me break him out.

472
00:19:08,320 --> 00:19:09,520
Damn, look at your stupid face.

473
00:19:09,520 --> 00:19:10,960
Do you know how to talk?

474
00:19:11,200 --> 00:19:11,920
If you can't speak properly,

475
00:19:11,920 --> 00:19:13,080
shut your trap.

476
00:19:13,440 --> 00:19:14,200
What kind of talk is that?

477
00:19:14,200 --> 00:19:15,360
So irritating!

478
00:19:15,720 --> 00:19:16,560
Who are you?

479
00:19:16,560 --> 00:19:17,600
What do you mean 'who am I'?

480
00:19:17,600 --> 00:19:18,600
What are you looking at?

481
00:19:18,600 --> 00:19:19,360
I'm looking at you, so what?

482
00:19:19,360 --> 00:19:21,000
What do you mean 'so what'?

483
00:19:21,080 --> 00:19:21,810
Don't hit me!

484
00:19:23,680 --> 00:19:24,540
Stop fighting!

485
00:19:25,120 --> 00:19:26,440
No, no, stop!

486
00:19:27,400 --> 00:19:27,880
He's biting me!

487
00:19:27,880 --> 00:19:28,610
Stop biting!

488
00:19:28,720 --> 00:19:31,160
Stop fighting!

489
00:19:50,280 --> 00:19:51,720
Uncle, hurry up!

490
00:19:51,720 --> 00:19:53,580
Everyone's already downstairs.

491
00:20:00,560 --> 00:20:01,360
Bro.

492
00:20:02,000 --> 00:20:02,480
Hey.

493
00:20:03,560 --> 00:20:04,680
You! Get down here!

494
00:20:12,000 --> 00:20:14,360
Don't go!

495
00:20:17,000 --> 00:20:18,800
Take one more step and I'll jump.

496
00:20:19,960 --> 00:20:21,020
What are you doing?

497
00:20:22,800 --> 00:20:23,720
Can't you tell?

498
00:20:24,200 --> 00:20:25,200
Jumping off?

499
00:20:26,080 --> 00:20:27,480
Fine. I won't interrupt your business.

500
00:20:27,480 --> 00:20:28,360
Listen.

501
00:20:28,360 --> 00:20:28,920
I need to ask you something.

502
00:20:28,920 --> 00:20:30,160
Can I ask before you jump?

503
00:20:30,160 --> 00:20:30,920
Go ahead.

504
00:20:31,280 --> 00:20:32,400
Weren't you

505
00:20:32,680 --> 00:20:34,600
shouting orders on the phone,

506
00:20:34,800 --> 00:20:36,400
dragging me all the way here

507
00:20:36,720 --> 00:20:37,640
just to watch you

508
00:20:37,640 --> 00:20:38,840
livestream your suicide?

509
00:20:38,840 --> 00:20:40,200
You're the one who pushed me to this.

510
00:20:40,200 --> 00:20:41,480
Who pushed you?

511
00:20:41,720 --> 00:20:42,520
I'm going to force you.

512
00:20:42,520 --> 00:20:44,520
I should make you jump from the 20th floor.

513
00:20:44,520 --> 00:20:45,880
Why would I make you jump from the 2nd floor?

514
00:20:45,880 --> 00:20:47,160
Am I crazy?

515
00:20:47,480 --> 00:20:49,000
I won't die jumping headfirst from the 2nd floor.

516
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:50,360
If I die, you'll have to pay with your life.

517
00:20:50,360 --> 00:20:51,160
Pay?

518
00:20:51,720 --> 00:20:53,240
If you really die today,

519
00:20:53,240 --> 00:20:55,040
I'll really pay with my life, okay?

520
00:20:55,040 --> 00:20:56,040
Go ahead and jump.

521
00:20:59,880 --> 00:21:00,960
Too scared to jump?

522
00:21:01,880 --> 00:21:03,880
If you don't dare to jump, then listen,

523
00:21:03,880 --> 00:21:06,440
pay back what you owe me today.

524
00:21:07,320 --> 00:21:08,980
Then I'll livestream for you.

525
00:21:09,120 --> 00:21:11,280
I'll jump instead, okay?

526
00:21:11,280 --> 00:21:12,040
Come on.

527
00:21:12,040 --> 00:21:13,440
I'll go up there.

528
00:21:13,640 --> 00:21:14,240
Don't pull this on me.

529
00:21:14,240 --> 00:21:15,400
Pay me back and I'll come down.

530
00:21:15,400 --> 00:21:15,920
No, no, no.

531
00:21:15,920 --> 00:21:16,880
Come on.

532
00:21:16,880 --> 00:21:18,410
Don't pull this stunt on me.

533
00:21:18,480 --> 00:21:19,480
What stunt?

534
00:21:19,480 --> 00:21:21,320
Do you really think I won't jump?

535
00:21:27,760 --> 00:21:29,680
No, you think I'm afraid of you, don't you?

536
00:21:29,680 --> 00:21:31,040
How could I be afraid of you?

537
00:21:31,040 --> 00:21:33,300
Come on, jump. I'll sit right here today.

538
00:21:33,480 --> 00:21:35,480
I'll watch you jump with my own eyes.

539
00:21:37,120 --> 00:21:39,000
So you're really going to jump today?

540
00:21:39,000 --> 00:21:40,000
I'll give you a discount.

541
00:21:40,000 --> 00:21:40,760
How's that?

542
00:21:40,840 --> 00:21:41,600
How much?

543
00:21:41,800 --> 00:21:42,480
3,000.

544
00:21:43,680 --> 00:21:44,320
I'll consider it payment

545
00:21:44,320 --> 00:21:46,180
for my boys to watch a monkey show.

546
00:21:46,520 --> 00:21:47,280
Deal?

547
00:21:47,280 --> 00:21:48,200
Deal.

548
00:21:48,440 --> 00:21:48,900
Come on.

549
00:21:50,560 --> 00:21:52,360
Look at you every day,

550
00:21:52,760 --> 00:21:53,720
acting like you're from a TV show,

551
00:21:53,720 --> 00:21:54,880
like Ke Zhen'e.

552
00:21:55,160 --> 00:21:56,620
Talking the toughest game

553
00:21:56,680 --> 00:21:58,120
then taking the worst beating.

554
00:21:58,120 --> 00:21:59,580
What kind of habit is this?

555
00:21:59,720 --> 00:22:00,980
Are you addicted to it?

556
00:22:01,160 --> 00:22:02,420
Are you jumping or not?

557
00:22:02,760 --> 00:22:03,280
Are you going to jump?

558
00:22:03,280 --> 00:22:04,000
Don't mess around.

559
00:22:04,000 --> 00:22:04,400
Jump or not?

560
00:22:04,400 --> 00:22:05,240
Stop messing with me.

561
00:22:05,240 --> 00:22:06,440
Who's messing with you? Jump!

562
00:22:06,440 --> 00:22:06,960
I said I'm messing with you.

563
00:22:06,960 --> 00:22:07,440
Stop!

564
00:22:27,080 --> 00:22:28,740
Are these three your friends?

565
00:22:30,960 --> 00:22:32,760
What kind of people are these?

566
00:22:39,000 --> 00:22:41,400
Young man, you need to speak politely.

567
00:22:41,680 --> 00:22:42,740
Show some respect.

568
00:22:48,400 --> 00:22:49,480
I'm his uncle.

569
00:22:55,040 --> 00:22:55,560
No.

570
00:22:55,880 --> 00:22:57,080
You look only

571
00:22:57,560 --> 00:22:58,890
about 30 or 40 years old.

572
00:22:59,440 --> 00:23:00,200
How can you be

573
00:23:00,200 --> 00:23:00,720
Tell me

574
00:23:00,720 --> 00:23:02,320
who you used to hang out with.

575
00:23:02,360 --> 00:23:03,360
After you tell me,

576
00:23:03,360 --> 00:23:05,120
I'll see if I know them.

577
00:23:08,120 --> 00:23:08,640
Well, I

578
00:23:10,080 --> 00:23:12,200
like to study Buddhism in my spare time.

579
00:23:12,200 --> 00:23:13,880
If you ask who I hang out with,

580
00:23:14,920 --> 00:23:16,440
let's just say monks.

581
00:23:18,880 --> 00:23:21,080
Which organization are you three from?

582
00:23:21,640 --> 00:23:23,160
The Sunset Years Club?

583
