00:35:35,000 --> 00:35:36,480
Five in the morning by the river.

869
00:35:36,480 --> 00:35:37,080
The Zhen position.

870
00:35:37,080 --> 00:35:38,880
You told me to burn three yellow talismans

871
00:35:38,880 --> 00:35:40,000
that would rise to the heavens.

872
00:35:40,000 --> 00:35:41,720
Then wash my hands in the river.

873
00:35:41,720 --> 00:35:42,800
And then it was done.

874
00:35:42,800 --> 00:35:45,240
You told me I'd never worry about food or clothing,

875
00:35:45,240 --> 00:35:46,880
that I'd be successful in my later years

876
00:35:46,880 --> 00:35:48,000
and become famous.

877
00:35:48,000 --> 00:35:49,120
Isn't that what you said?

878
00:35:49,120 --> 00:35:49,880
Remember?

879
00:35:50,880 --> 00:35:51,740
I remember now.

880
00:35:52,000 --> 00:35:53,400
Was my prediction wrong?

881
00:35:53,440 --> 00:35:54,040
I admit it.

882
00:35:54,400 --> 00:35:55,440
So you admit it?

883
00:35:55,440 --> 00:35:55,800
I admit it.

884
00:35:55,800 --> 00:35:56,720
Let's go to the police station.

885
00:35:56,720 --> 00:35:57,250
What for?

886
00:35:57,400 --> 00:35:58,320
Why should I go to the police station?

887
00:35:58,320 --> 00:35:58,960
What? Why?

888
00:35:58,960 --> 00:35:59,480
Go to the police station?

889
00:35:59,480 --> 00:36:00,600
What police station? What for?

890
00:36:00,600 --> 00:36:01,400
Do you know?

891
00:36:01,680 --> 00:36:02,360
Do you know who I am?

892
00:36:02,360 --> 00:36:03,560
Just because of those few words you said,

893
00:36:03,560 --> 00:36:06,000
I spent over ten years in prison.

894
00:36:06,000 --> 00:36:07,600
Over ten years behind bars!

895
00:36:07,600 --> 00:36:08,440
What did you do

896
00:36:08,440 --> 00:36:09,560
to get locked up for so long?

897
00:36:09,560 --> 00:36:10,960
I didn't do anything!

898
00:36:10,960 --> 00:36:11,840
I did exactly what you told me.

899
00:36:11,840 --> 00:36:12,760
I threw a knife in there.

900
00:36:12,760 --> 00:36:14,490
The day after I threw the knife,

901
00:36:15,000 --> 00:36:16,800
a female corpse floated up.

902
00:36:17,080 --> 00:36:18,400
How could I explain that to the police?

903
00:36:18,400 --> 00:36:19,680
I told them it was a fortune teller

904
00:36:19,680 --> 00:36:20,480
who told me to do it.

905
00:36:20,480 --> 00:36:21,760
I told them everything.

906
00:36:21,760 --> 00:36:23,160
After I told them, they went looking for you

907
00:36:23,160 --> 00:36:24,040
but couldn't find you. Where did you go?

908
00:36:24,040 --> 00:36:26,080
Where were you?

909
00:36:26,080 --> 00:36:27,280
Wandering the world.

910
00:36:29,400 --> 00:36:30,160
Where else can I go?

911
00:36:30,160 --> 00:36:30,480
What are you doing here?

912
00:36:30,480 --> 00:36:31,480
Why are you looking for me?

913
00:36:31,480 --> 00:36:32,200
You're here for money.

914
00:36:32,200 --> 00:36:32,960
More than 20 years have passed.

915
00:36:32,960 --> 00:36:34,320
Let's go to the police station.

916
00:36:34,320 --> 00:36:34,880
I won't go.

917
00:36:34,880 --> 00:36:36,240
Go? What would I do at the police station?

918
00:36:36,240 --> 00:36:36,840
Me at the police station?

919
00:36:36,840 --> 00:36:38,640
Can I report you for feudal superstition?

920
00:36:38,640 --> 00:36:40,960
I'm just asking if my fortune-telling was accurate.

921
00:36:40,960 --> 00:36:42,000
What accuracy are you talking about?

922
00:36:42,000 --> 00:36:43,880
You spent over ten years in prison.

923
00:36:43,880 --> 00:36:44,800
While you were in there,

924
00:36:44,800 --> 00:36:46,000
didn't they feed you?

925
00:36:47,000 --> 00:36:49,130
Didn't they give you uniforms to wear?

926
00:36:54,880 --> 00:36:56,340
Nothing to say now, right?

927
00:36:58,200 --> 00:36:59,280
You call that

928
00:36:59,920 --> 00:37:01,160
living without worries?

929
00:37:01,160 --> 00:37:02,320
Living comfortably.

930
00:37:02,320 --> 00:37:03,120
That's what I call.

931
00:37:03,120 --> 00:37:03,760
So what?

932
00:37:03,840 --> 00:37:05,240
One day this case gets overturned.

933
00:37:05,240 --> 00:37:07,040
The internet is so powerful nowadays.

934
00:37:07,040 --> 00:37:07,720
Once the case is overturned,

935
00:37:07,720 --> 00:37:09,840
you'll become famous throughout the world.

936
00:37:09,840 --> 00:37:11,080
What's wrong with that?

937
00:37:11,080 --> 00:37:12,080
Can I just kill him?

938
00:37:12,080 --> 00:37:13,440
No, no, no. Calm down first.

939
00:37:13,440 --> 00:37:14,480
No, I've already been sentenced to more than 10 years.

940
00:37:14,480 --> 00:37:15,680
If I beat him up, that's what he'll get.

941
00:37:15,680 --> 00:37:18,360
That makes sense in theory and logic.

942
00:37:18,600 --> 00:37:19,880
Whose side are you on anyway?

943
00:37:19,880 --> 00:37:22,560
Beating or cursing him now won't help.

944
00:37:22,560 --> 00:37:24,290
You might end up back in prison.

945
00:37:24,400 --> 00:37:25,600
What you should do now

946
00:37:25,760 --> 00:37:27,520
is bring him to the police station.

947
00:37:27,520 --> 00:37:28,580
To testify for you.

948
00:37:29,360 --> 00:37:30,280
On your part,

949
00:37:30,840 --> 00:37:32,640
he really spent over a decade in prison

950
00:37:32,640 --> 00:37:34,000
because of what you said.

951
00:37:34,000 --> 00:37:35,440
We're still appealing the case.

952
00:37:35,440 --> 00:37:36,900
So we need your statement.

953
00:37:36,920 --> 00:37:37,920
Once you're there,

954
00:37:37,920 --> 00:37:39,440
you'll only talk about his case.

955
00:37:39,440 --> 00:37:40,760
Whatever you've done in the past

956
00:37:40,760 --> 00:37:42,000
has nothing to do with this.

957
00:37:42,000 --> 00:37:43,400
You're a fortune teller.

958
00:37:43,520 --> 00:37:44,360
I believe

959
00:37:44,560 --> 00:37:45,840
and you believe too

960
00:37:46,360 --> 00:37:47,420
that karma exists,

961
00:37:47,480 --> 00:37:48,000
right?

962
00:37:53,080 --> 00:37:54,000
Dapao.

963
00:37:54,440 --> 00:37:55,240
What?

964
00:37:56,880 --> 00:37:57,640
Take this.

965
00:37:58,000 --> 00:37:58,930
What's this for?

966
00:37:59,440 --> 00:38:00,080
Take it.

967
00:38:00,680 --> 00:38:02,720
I took 50 yuan from you back then.

968
00:38:03,440 --> 00:38:04,700
Now I'm giving it back.

969
00:38:05,720 --> 00:38:06,960
But prices have changed.

970
00:38:06,960 --> 00:38:09,090
Why are you bringing this nonsense up?

971
00:38:09,120 --> 00:38:09,720
Even now,

972
00:38:09,720 --> 00:38:11,640
I still believe my fortune-telling was correct.

973
00:38:11,640 --> 00:38:12,840
It was clearly about you.

974
00:38:12,840 --> 00:38:13,440
Free from worries about food and clothing,

975
00:38:13,440 --> 00:38:14,640
living comfortably.

976
00:38:14,880 --> 00:38:17,080
How dare you mention this?

977
00:38:18,640 --> 00:38:20,200
I need to have the courage to tell you what comes next.

978
00:38:20,200 --> 00:38:21,240
Remember this:

979
00:38:21,440 --> 00:38:22,720
The day of vindication

980
00:38:22,720 --> 00:38:24,320
will be when you become famous

981
00:38:24,320 --> 00:38:26,250
and renowned throughout the land.

982
00:38:27,520 --> 00:38:29,440
What about my fortune-telling fee?

983
00:38:29,440 --> 00:38:30,700
I'll give it to you too.

984
00:38:31,520 --> 00:38:32,780
Let's talk about fate.

985
00:38:33,600 --> 00:38:34,640
Come visit me often in the future.

986
00:38:34,640 --> 00:38:35,880
Keep coming back here,

987
00:38:35,880 --> 00:38:37,000
I'll continue for free.

988
00:38:37,000 --> 00:38:38,160
No need for free service.

989
00:38:38,160 --> 00:38:40,200
Next time when I need you to testify,

990
00:38:40,200 --> 00:38:41,160
just show up.

991
00:38:42,280 --> 00:38:43,040
About testifying,

992
00:38:43,040 --> 00:38:44,640
I'll come whenever you call.

993
00:38:45,520 --> 00:38:46,880
But brother, you...

994
00:38:50,200 --> 00:38:51,320
Brother, what's

995
00:38:51,760 --> 00:38:52,560
wrong with me?

996
00:38:52,760 --> 00:38:54,440
You might face a calamity.

997
00:38:55,600 --> 00:38:56,640
Can it be avoided?

998
00:38:58,040 --> 00:38:59,280
Life in this world

999
00:38:59,800 --> 00:39:01,260
is nothing but suffering.

1000
00:39:02,200 --> 00:39:03,530
Finding release sooner

1001
00:39:04,080 --> 00:39:06,040
might not be such a bad thing.

1002
00:39:43,920 --> 00:39:44,600
Erpang.

1003
00:39:57,000 --> 00:39:57,640
Erpang.

1004
00:40:06,400 --> 00:40:07,000
Erpang.

1005
00:40:30,320 --> 00:40:31,840
I thought you really committed suicide.

1006
00:40:31,840 --> 00:40:34,040
I thought debt collectors had chased me all the way here.

1007
00:40:34,040 --> 00:40:35,080
How could you get instant noodles

1008
00:40:35,080 --> 00:40:36,280
all over your head?

1009
00:40:37,560 --> 00:40:39,020
Why didn't you make a fire?

1010
00:40:39,200 --> 00:40:40,480
I don't know how.

1011
00:40:40,960 --> 00:40:43,490
The fire went out soon after you left that day.

1012
00:40:45,160 --> 00:40:46,200
Then how did you cook the noodles?

1013
00:40:46,200 --> 00:40:47,160
I didn't cook them.

1014
00:40:47,160 --> 00:40:48,200
I ate them dry.

1015
00:40:48,200 --> 00:40:49,640
Then a bite of noodles and a sip of wine.

1016
00:40:49,640 --> 00:40:50,760
A bite of noodles and a sip of wine.

1017
00:40:50,760 --> 00:40:51,920
It's quite satisfying.

1018
00:40:51,920 --> 00:40:53,480
The biggest difference between us and animals is

1019
00:40:53,480 --> 00:40:55,010
that we know how to use fire.

1020
00:40:55,480 --> 00:40:56,560
I know how to use fire too.

1021
00:40:56,560 --> 00:40:57,960
But there's no fire here.

1022
00:41:01,000 --> 00:41:02,530
There'll be hot food later.

1023
00:41:03,040 --> 00:41:04,840
I'll just have a few bites first.

1024
00:41:05,640 --> 00:41:07,840
How long has it been since you've eaten?

1025
00:41:09,280 --> 00:41:10,280
I can't remember.

1026
00:41:10,400 --> 00:41:11,400
Two or three days.

1027
00:41:11,640 --> 00:41:12,770
Maybe three or four.

1028
00:41:13,360 --> 00:41:14,760
Time passes easily in the mountains,

1029
00:41:14,760 --> 00:41:18,220
while a thousand years of prosperity have passed in the world.

1030
00:41:19,880 --> 00:41:21,480
With that attitude of yours,

1031
00:41:21,480 --> 00:41:24,280
you wouldn't starve even if you didn't eat for ten years.

1032
00:41:24,280 --> 00:41:26,410
When did your phone get disconnected?

1033
00:41:26,480 --> 00:41:27,610
I really don't know.

1034
00:41:28,160 --> 00:41:29,840
I think it's actually better this way.

1035
00:41:29,840 --> 00:41:31,840
Saves me from all those annoying calls.

1036
00:41:31,840 --> 00:41:33,370
Don't just eat by yourself.

1037
00:41:33,720 --> 00:41:35,040
How long have the dogs gone without food?

1038
00:41:35,040 --> 00:41:35,960
I haven't eaten for days.

1039
00:41:35,960 --> 00:41:37,880
So they haven't eaten for days either.

1040
00:41:37,880 --> 00:41:39,160
Uncle, if you hadn't come,

1041
00:41:39,160 --> 00:41:41,420
we would've all starved to death up here.

1042
00:41:44,040 --> 00:41:45,400
Hurry up and grab a sausage

1043
00:41:45,400 --> 00:41:47,130
to satisfy their hunger first.

1044
00:41:47,240 --> 00:41:48,970
I'll cook you all a proper meal.

1045
00:42:21,440 --> 00:42:23,040
The steps and methods for lighting the stove

1046
00:42:23,040 --> 00:42:24,280
Have you got it all clear?

1047
00:42:24,280 --> 00:42:25,010
Yes, I got it.

1048
00:42:28,840 --> 00:42:29,360
Uncle.

1049
00:42:30,600 --> 00:42:32,720
Actually, these quilts are thick enough.

1050
00:42:32,720 --> 00:42:33,480
As long as I don't turn over,

1051
00:42:33,480 --> 00:42:34,810
I won't feel cold at all.

1052
00:42:35,000 --> 00:42:36,000
I just can't stick out of the covers.

1053
00:42:36,000 --> 00:42:37,440
It's too miserable when I do.

1054
00:42:37,440 --> 00:42:39,480
Anyway, I've taught you how to light the stove.

1055
00:42:39,480 --> 00:42:41,410
Whether you do it or not is up to you.

1056
00:42:46,200 --> 00:42:46,840
Here you go.

1057
00:42:46,840 --> 00:42:48,300
Is today Spring Festival?

1058
00:42:48,480 --> 00:42:49,240
Tomorrow.

1059
00:42:51,240 --> 00:42:52,240
Tomorrow.

1060
00:42:52,360 --> 00:42:53,760
Mengmeng is coming back.

1061
00:42:53,840 --> 00:42:55,560
I'll celebrate the New Year with her.

1062
00:42:55,560 --> 00:42:56,290
Originally,

1063
00:42:56,800 --> 00:42:58,200
we should be together,

1064
00:42:58,600 --> 00:43:00,000
but I'm afraid if you're here,

1065
00:43:00,000 --> 00:43:01,360
the creditors might come too,

1066
00:43:01,360 --> 00:43:03,290
and that would frighten Mengmeng.

1067
00:43:03,800 --> 00:43:05,600
Why is Mengmeng still so fragile?

1068
00:43:05,600 --> 00:43:06,730
You're not fragile.

1069
00:43:07,120 --> 00:43:07,840
You're not fragile.

1070
00:43:07,840 --> 00:43:08,680
You're hiding in the mountains.
